snippet.title: Rustle - Ambient VR Game [Trailer]
snippet.description:
Download & learn more here: https://antoine-ramo.itch.io/rustle

Rustle was developed in 3 months by a small team of students at the Cnam_Enjmin, in France.

Alice Rameau - Project coordinator & 2D/3D Artist

Thomas Foucault - Programmer

Antoine Lima De Carvalho - Game Designer

Minna Clair - UX/UR Designer

Antonin Terrien - Sound Designer

Enzo Giglio - Sound Designer

Rudy Michel - 3D Artist

Yann Kukolewsky - 2D Artist

Ora Yermia - Diane’s voice
